OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe Body Shop to shut      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnearly half of its UK      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstores                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Body Shop is set to shut nearly    
OL,6, half of its 198 stores in the UK and   
OL,7, reduce the size of its head office,    
OL,8, leading to hundreds of job losses.     
OL,10,FClosures will begin immediately on     
OL,11,FTuesday, according to the firm that is 
OL,12,Foverseeing the restructuring of the    
OL,13,Fretailer.                              
OL,15,FThe Body Shop employs around 2,200     
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK, including 750 staff  
OL,17,Fat its head office.                    
OL,19,FThe cuts would "help re-energise" the  
OL,20,Fbrand, the administrators said.        
